title: Episode 131: Baron Cruz - Becoming High Status
description:
On this interview Robbie and Baron Cruz from super popular YouTube Channel - The Charisma Matrix discuss how to be perceived as high status and confident by maximizing your voice and sub-communication. Baron also shares some amazing advice to become quick and witty in conversations when people try to dominate or bully you instead of freezing up.

Show Notes:
The key to starting a successful YouTube channel and how Barron started his with Home Depot floodlights (03:00)
How to succeed in front of the camera if you’re shy and timid… (06:30)
What impact does playing organized team sports as a kid have on your social skills and confidence (12:00)
The two components of your voice that will have a game changing impact on your confidence… (15:30)
What should you do if you have an unattractive accent… (17:30)
“Just be yourself…” good advice or bad?… (19:00)
Should you take risks and be authentic on social media in our current cancel culture filled with social justice warriors and snowflakes… (23:30)
An epic strategy to start a channel where you’ll never run out of content without having to think and be creative…(29:00)
How to avoid freezing up and not knowing what to say when someone makes fun of you or tries to knock you in conversation… (32:30)
What can you do if you feel like you naturally have a weak voice… (37:00)
How to avoid being perceived as supplicating and low status… (42:00)
Tai Lopez vs. Grand Cardone - who is more confident, powerful and high status? (44:00)
How to re-establish the conversation equilibrium if someone acts like they are higher status than you… (47:30)
Warning, avoid the trap of acting ____ while trying to become more high status… (52:30)
The difference between someone who is truly high status vs. trying to be high status… (55:45)

The Charisma Matrix

I'm Robbie Kramer 🎙Host of The Inner Confidence Podcast & Founder of Inner Confidence, Inc.

I lived an exhilarating single life filled with adventures and lessons, and ultimately achieved what I had always aspired to – finding an amazing, feminine, and loving wife. 

I believe my experiences provide a rare balance of wild freedom and committed love, equipping me with the insights to help you navigate the complexities of dating and relationships in today's world. Let me guide you to embrace your desires, improve your social prowess, and ultimately attract the partner who aligns with your highest aspirations.

You won’t find any fluffy, new-age, or cringy stuff here, just tested, proven and actionable advice that yields results.

Apply to join our exclusive Inner Confidence Community of ambitious men who are actively working together to achieve their goals faster   ► https://innerconfidence.com/community

You can email me at robbie@innerconfidence.com with any questions or comments.
